---
// Brand-promise signature moment. The big UNPLUG type isn't decoration -
// it's the literal name of the company AND the promise the rest of the
// page is selling. This rebuild puts it in context: what unplug actually
// means here, three proof points, and a direct CTA.
//
// Dark full-bleed photo backdrop, sun-gold accent rule above the headline,
// proof grid with rule dividers, dark-on-dark CTA with sun-gold outline.
---

<section class="relative bg-surface-warm text-ink overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="/img/source/destinations/catamaran-anchorage-sunset-bvi-01.jpg"
    alt=""
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40"
  />
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(31,27,23,0.55) 0%, rgba(31,27,23,0.95) 75%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-14 py-28 sm:py-36 lg:py-44 text-center">
    <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-sun mx-auto mb-8" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.625rem] font-semibold text-sun mb-10">
      What you actually get when you do
    </p>

    {/* The brand wordmark at maximum scale - this IS the company name AND
         the promise the site is built around. */}
    <h2
      class="font-display text-ink font-extralight leading-[0.85] tracking-[-0.05em]"
      style="font-size: clamp(5rem, 16vw, 14rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      UNPLUG
    </h2>

    <p
      class="font-serif-quote italic mt-10 lg:mt-12 text-[1.25rem] lg:text-[1.625rem] leading-[1.45] tracking-[-0.015em] text-ink/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-balance"
      style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 1;"
    >
      Just bringing life back down to zero. Reset your body and mind, on nothing but water, weather, and time.
    </p>

    {/* Three concrete proof points - what "unplug" actually looks like
         in practice. Hairline dividers in sun-gold tint. */}
    <ul class="mt-14 lg:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 max-w-3xl mx-auto divide-y sm:divide-y-0 sm:divide-x divide-ink/15 border-y border-ink/15">
      <li class="px-6 py-8">
        <p class="font-display text-[2rem] text-sun leading-none" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;">Wednesday</p>
        <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[0.5625rem] font-semibold text-ink/70 mt-3">
          The day the signal finally drops
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="px-6 py-8">
        <p class="font-display text-[2rem] text-sun leading-none" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;">4 hours</p>
        <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[0.5625rem] font-semibold text-ink/70 mt-3">
          Longest passage you'll ever sit through
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="px-6 py-8">
        <p class="font-display text-[2rem] text-sun leading-none" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;">Zero</p>
        <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[0.5625rem] font-semibold text-ink/70 mt-3">
          Items billed after the deposit
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-14 lg:mt-16">
      <a
        href="/calendar"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-ink border-b-2 border-sun pb-1 hover:text-sun transition-colors"
      >
        Find Your Week
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M1 8h13M9 3l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
